These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, skateboard, motorbike, taxi
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person driving the skateboard##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Transport      | motorbike  | skateboard | taxi        | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, june, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's birthday is in june##7
2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
3. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Birthday     | june | november       | may         | february     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, journalist, musician, nurse
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the nurse is somewhere between the journalist and the police-officer##7
3. the musician is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the police-officer is somewhere between the nurse and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Job   | musician | police-officer  | nurse   | journalist |

