.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, begonia, rose
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growsdaisy##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower         | begonia | daisy   | rose | tulip |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

