.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
House: cottage, cape-cod, farmhouse, tower
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the tower house##3
6. the tower house is somewhere between the cottage house and the cape-cod house##7
7. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| House   | cottage    | tower | cape-cod   | farmhouse |

