.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, engineer, writer, security-guard
1. the lawyer is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the security-guard is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the security-guard is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Job   | lawyer | writer | security-guard    | engineer |

