.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, scientist, security-guard
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, singing, video-games, chess
1. the engineer is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
2. the scientist is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the scientist is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the police-officer##7
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| Hobby   | chess         | video-games      | drawing | singing            |

