1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person who growspoppy##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the person who growssunflower##6
3. the person who growsdahlia is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Flower           | zinnia    | dahlia   | poppy  | sunflower      |

