.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, red, lilac, yellow
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who likes red and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person who likes red##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Color   | yellow | fuchsia | red | lilac   |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | soul      | gospel      | trance |

