.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
4 different games are played: chess, whist, backgammon, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, subway, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing bridge is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing backgammon is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person playing backgammon##7
7. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Game       | bridge | chess | whist | backgammon |
| Transport   | bike   | trike      | bus        | subway  |

