3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
6. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
