.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, whist, snooker
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Game   | whist | snooker  | domino | bridge |

 